      "title": "Shagala as a member of the National List of the United Nations Party?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to reports, the names of Sagala Ratnayaka, Akilaviraj Kariyawasam and Ruvan Wijewardena have been nominated for the vacant post of United National Party National List Member of Parliament after Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as President.",
        "However, political information suggests that one of these three, Sagala Ratnayaka or Ruvan Wijewardena, will get a chance to become a member of the national list."
